About this item

  • Rechargeable Flashlight: Powerful flashlight 100000 lumens, throw up to 1350Metres (Nearly 4429ft). Uses 18pcs XHP70.2 LEDs, 50X times brighter than ordinary car lights. Good for power outage, camping, hiking, caving, exploring etc.
  • Super Bright 8 Modes: Ultra wide beam effortlessly illuminates a whole room or backyard. 8 settings replace the need for multiple flashlights:(700lm/2000lm/5000lm/10,000lm/22,000lm|30,000lm/60,000lm/100,000lm/ and 2 special mode: Turbo and Strobe). And this led flashlight is powered by a rechargeable battery pack (included) which helps save the battery cost and is very environmental friendly. Makes for a practical addition to any household or emergency kit.
  • Flashlight for Emergencies: MS18 high powered flashlight is equipped with high capacity rechargeable battery pack, providing up to 14 hours of runtime in low mode, service life can reach to 50,000 hours. This led flashlight rechargeable high lumens can solve your urgent needs.
  • User-Friendly Design: digital screen of the bright flashlight will display its electricity level, then we know clearly how much power of battery is still there.
  • High Performance: This MS18 powerful flashlight is rechargeable, made of high performance aluminum alloy, sturdy and durable,designed to be virtually indestructible. First flashlight with heat pipe cooling system(cooling fans), ensure the high performance and longer runtime on high output. And it is IP56 waterproof and dustproof, which make the flashlight more durable and tough.
  • Friendly Service: For first use, please take out the battery protection pcs.(it is between flashlight head and battery pack). And fully charged the battery pack. If you have any questions during using the flashlight, please contact us.

Powerful Led Flashlight

  • Imalent MS18 is a powerful led flashlight and versatile option that is great for outdoor activities, search, rescue, hiking, camping, and emergency situations.
  • Its impressive brightness, long beam distance, and durable construction make it a top performer among high-powered flashlights.

Brightest Flashlight in the World

  • Imalent MS18 is the brightest flashlight, maximum output of 100,000 lumens. Ideal for illuminating large areas, signaling for help, or searching for lost items or individuals.
  • The maximum beam distance of up to 1350 meters, allowing you to see clearly in the dark over long distances.

Why my MS18 doesn't work?

For first use, please take out the flashlight protection pcs.(it is between flashlight head and flashlight body). Then, screw it as tightly as you can.

How to use the lockout?

When you see the lock sign on the OLED display, you can quickly click five times, until you see the unlock sign.

Does the fan be operated to a certain degree or when I start it?

When the MS18 flashlight body internal temperature reaches 70 degrees celsius, the fans will be activate automatic to cool down.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Rene Gonzalez
5.0 out of 5 stars Lumen powerhouse or 55 hour runtime.
Reviewed in the United States on August 26, 2019
Verified Purchase
I purchased both the Imalent MS12 and MS18 since i have been searching for a replacement for my older 2012 era 2,300 lumen flashlight whose model includes the word monster in it.

The lumen output of the MS18 at its turbo 100,000 lumen setting is nothing less than remarkable. Yet i have always enjoyed having a wider range of battery lifespan and lumen options in my flashlights. For this reason i decided to keep the MS12 model. I decided to give the MS18 to my cousin as a thank you gift which he loved. The MS18 has a couple pluses over the MS12 like an OLED screen, improved cooling system and almost twice the lumen output in turbo mode.

My favorite setting on the MS12 which was a deciding factor for me is the low setting at 300 lumens. This low setting is more than enough to eluminate a large room by placing the flashlight in the center of the room pointing upwards at the most familiar white colored ceilings of most homes. The fact that it can run on the lowest setting for an impressive 55 hours is remarkable. There is no heat generated at the lowest setting and the cooling fan does not activate while in this setting.

My cousin did a 20 minute test with both the MS12 and MS18 at night outside his house. He let me know that the cooling system on the MS12 on turbo simply cannot keep up and the entire flaslight becomes too hot to touch without using leather gloves. He also let me know that the cooling system on his MS18 on turbo is greatly improved and keeps the flashlight at a tolerable temperature. A neat fact is that the MS18 had a higher beam intensity than the sunlight during a 95 degree midday in San Jose California in August.

I plan to use the included clear plastic battery protector while not in use to prolong the inevitable self discharge rate. I also plan to top up the battery pack every three to four months.

These flaslight are not small or lightweight so i highly recommend that the included shoulderstrap be used. They are also incredibly powerful and most definitely not a toy so always be careful while using the higher settings.

It is wonderful to know that i have 55 hours of room lighting in case of an emergency or power outage.
